Bolt Builds is a full-service Design + Build firm and fully insured General Contractor based in Brooklyn. We specialize in design-forward hospitality, retail, and residential projects that merge classical sensibility with innovative construction and fabrication methods. We believe that great design is only as strong as its execution — and that means being just as rigorous about budgets, schedules, and communication as we are about creative vision.

The Role
We’re looking for a Senior Project Manager to lead high-caliber design+build projects from pre-construction through closeout. This is a senior leadership role focused not just on coordination, but true ownership of the budget, the timeline, the client relationship, and the finished product. You’ll serve as the primary point of contact for clients and consultants, guiding them through every stage of the process with clarity and confidence. Internally, you’ll collaborate with our design, construction, and fabrication consultants to ensure seamless execution and mentor junior team members along the way. You’ll be accountable for delivering exceptional projects on time and on budget, while protecting both creative intent and financial integrity."/><meta property="og:image" content="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/4j6lg3tu/production/52652e63365208885f555c81484ff15eb2155f66-1447x859.jpg"/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Bolt"/><meta property="og:locale" content="en_US"/><meta name="next-head-count" content="14"/><link data-next-font="" rel="preconnect" href="../index.html" crossorigin="anonymous"/><link rel="preload" href="../_next/static/css/03654ae58a6f64c1.css" as="style"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="../_next/static/css/03654ae58a6f64c1.css" data-n-g=""/><noscript data-n-css=""></noscript><script defer="" nomodule="" src="../_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js"></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/webpack-6ef43a8d4a395f49.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/framework-64ad27b21261a9ce.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/main-fc56ac81e639fb5e.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/pages/_app-e847f18df79b2407.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/276-306ef570f072595a.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/874-5abf096eed7b4aea.js" defer=""></script><script src="../_next/static/chunks/pages/jobs/[slug]-